                                    <h2>Agenda</h2>
								</header>
                                 <p class="content">Detailed agenda + invited speakers and experts coming soon. </p>
								<ul>
									
										<li>LSST experts (Phil Marshall, Federica Bianco, Lynne Jones, or Zeljko Ivezic) will give opening talks about cadence constraints and strategies, the OpSim software, existing cadence simulations, and a summary of cadence structures that have already been explored (e.g., in <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1708.04058">Marshall et al. 2017</a>).
                                        </li>
									
										<li>
                                    Small groups of 3-4 people with different scientific interests will use computers with the OpSim software pre-installed to seek innovative cadence structures that satisfy all group members (by modifying existing simulations and/or running partial simulations)</li>
									
										<li>
                                    Groups will present their findings.  
                                    </li>  
								</ul>
								
								
